# Quiz App

QuizApp is allows admin to generate quizzes which will select questions from question bank randomly and saves quizzes. The user when he plays gets the random quiz from the quizzes the admin had generated

## View Questions [/getquestions]

### List All Questions [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "id": 1,
                "answer": "b",
                "answer1": "Mumbai",
                "answer2": "Delhi",
                "answer3": "Chennai",
                "answer4": "Bangalore",
                "categoryId": 1,
                "difficultyId": 1,
                "questionName": "What is the capital of India"
            }
        ]
        
