## Create Questions [/setquestions]

### Create a New Question [POST]

You may create your own question using this action. It takes all the parameters in the form and performs POST action

+ Request (application/json)

        {
                "id": 1,
                "answer": "b",
                "answer1": "Mumbai",
                "answer2": "Delhi",
                "answer3": "Chennai",
                "answer4": "Bangalore",
                "categoryId": 1,
